(31767, 'Andomatoid 2 mg 28 f.c.tabs.', 'اندوماتويد 2مجم 28 قرص', '', '1,100', 'Baricitinib', 'Eva pharma > andalous pharma', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'يستخدم لعلاج التهاب المفاصل الروماتويدي (الحالة التي يهاجم فيها الجسم مفاصله مما يسبب الألم والتورم وفقدان الوظيفة).', 'Janus kinase (jak) inhibitor', '2 mg', 'In the US and Europe, baricitinib is indicated for the treatment of adult patients with moderately to severely active rheumatoid arthritis who have had an inadequate response to one or more TNF blockers. Baricitinib may be used as monotherapy or in combination with [methotrexate] [L41760,L41770] or other DMARDs.[L41760]
