(22327, 'Marrital lotion 120 ml', 'ماريتال لوشن 120 ملي', '', '39', 'Zinc oxide+olive oil+panthenol+chamomile ext+aloe vera ext+vitamin e+nigella sativa oil', 'Egyptian company for cosmetics > fusion pharm', 'Lotion', 'لوشن', 'مرطب و ملطف للجلد-- لعلاج جفاف الجلد -- لتخفيف حكة الجلد -- علاج حروق الشمس -- علاج طفح الحفاض', 'Moisturizing topicals', '120 ml', 'Zinc can be used for the treatment and prevention of zinc deficiency/its consequences, including stunted growth and acute diarrhea in children, and slowed wound healing. It is also utilized for boosting the immune system, treating the common cold and recurrent ear infections, as well as preventing lower respiratory tract infections [L2172].', '', '', 1453, '2022-05-12', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
