(29227, 'Viagra 100mg 4 f.c.tablets', 'فياجرا فايزر 100مجم 4 قرص', '100', '144', 'Sildenafil', 'Pfizer', 'Tablet', 'أقراص', 'مقوي للرجال', 'Tonic for men', '100mg', 'Sildenafil is a phosphodiesterase-5 (PDE5) inhibitor that is predominantly employed for two primary indications:
